Class FileLink.FileLinkInputStream

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.io.InputStream
      • org.apache.hadoop.hbase.io.FileLink.FileLinkInputStream
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable, org.apache.hadoop.fs.CanSetDropBehind, org.apache.hadoop.fs.CanSetReadahead, org.apache.hadoop.fs.PositionedReadable, org.apache.hadoop.fs.Seekable
    Enclosing class:
    FileLink

    private static class FileLink.FileLinkInputStream
extends InputStream
implements org.apache.hadoop.fs.Seekable, org.apache.hadoop.fs.PositionedReadable, org.apache.hadoop.fs.CanSetDropBehind, org.apache.hadoop.fs.CanSetReadahead
    FileLink InputStream that handles the switch between the original path and the alternative locations, when the file is moved.
